high_descs: turn right towards the bed stool
pick up the tray on the bed stool
turn around towards the table and then left towards the gas cooker
put the tray in the microwave above the gas cooker and heat it for 5 minutes then take it out
turn around and walk towards the door, then move right towards the bed stool
put the tray on the bed stool

high_descs: Turn to the right facing the table.
Grab the tray off of the table.
Turn to the right.  Go forward to the stove.
Open the microwave. Put the tray in the microwave.  Turn the microwave on.  Take the tray out when the microwave is finished.
Turn all the way around to the left.  Go towards the door.  At the door turn right.
Put the tray on the small black table to the left of the green object.
anns.task_desc: Warm a tray up to put on the table.

high_descs: Pick up the tray off of the shelves.
Turn around then head left to the stove.
Look up and warm the tray up in the microwave for 2 seconds.
Turn around and go back to the shelves.
Place the tray back on the shelves.
anns.task_desc: Place the warmed up tray back on the shelf.
